Grid is combination of intersection of main axis and cross axis 
Point of intersection is grid like it goes in both cross and main axis

grid template areas ----> Parent like flex box
grid-area (used to define the elements)

for evenly distribution in grid system
 fr(fraction)
 repeat(no of times,how much space(auto,1fr,etc)) Works for responsiveness too
 lg for very big screen
 md for laptop/pc
 md and sm both for tablets
 sm for mobiles

Positioning :-
 Default Static
 Fixed (Always on screen,attached to screen)
 Sticky (according to viewport)
 Relative (parent)
 Absolute(Child)


